com.team1389.command_framework.command_base

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team1389.command_framework.command_base.Command
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoNothingCommand, TurnAngleCommand, WaitForBooleanCommand

    public abstract class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    A command is an object that should be used in an iterative matter. It runs a step of itself in exec, and runs other methods at different points of the command's lifestyle.
    Author:
    Josh
